-- Xilinx Falls After Chipmaker Says Sales to Fall as Much as 9% This Quarter
-- B y   I a n   K i n g
-- 2010-12-21T21:40:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-21/xilinx-falls-after-chipmaker-says-sales-to-fall-as-much-as-9-this-quarter.html
Xilinx Inc. fell more than 5 percent
in extended trading after the chipmaker said sales will fall as
much as 9 percent this quarter from the previous period, more
than previously predicted, citing weak demand.  Xilinx, based in San Jose, California, had said revenue
would fall as much as 4 percent.  To contact the reporter on this story:
